Packages
--------

Collaborative filtering for Java.

  http://taste.sf.net/

Pyflix is a small package written in Python that provides an easy entry point
for getting up and running in the Netflix Prize competition. It combines an
efficient storage scheme with an intuitive high-level API that allows
contestants to focus on the real problem, the recommendation system algorithm.

  http://pyflix.python-hosting.com/

